{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/posts/algorithm/sort/","result":{"data":{"logo":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","width":400,"height":128,"src":"/static/2b5eaa0de166a8b5faebad4955c2200c/3891b/ghost-logo.png","srcSet":"/static/2b5eaa0de166a8b5faebad4955c2200c/3891b/ghost-logo.png 1x"}}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<ul>\n<li>프로그래머스에서 <a href=\"https://programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/42579\">베스트앨범</a> 문제를 풀다가 찾아보게 되었다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"간단한-정렬\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%84%EB%8B%A8%ED%95%9C-%EC%A0%95%EB%A0%AC\" aria-label=\"간단한 정렬 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>간단한 정렬</h1>\n<deckgo-highlight-code python  theme=\"one-dark\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">nums = [4,3,2,1,5]\nnums.sort()\nnums\n&gt;&gt; [1,2,3,4,5]</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<ul>\n<li>원본 데이터를 오름차순으로 정렬시킨다.</li>\n<li>리스트가 1차원이면서 원소가 primitive한 값일때만 제대로 정렬되는듯 하다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"특정-인덱스를-기준으로-정렬\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B9%EC%A0%95-%EC%9D%B8%EB%8D%B1%EC%8A%A4%EB%A5%BC-%EA%B8%B0%EC%A4%80%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EC%A0%95%EB%A0%AC\" aria-label=\"특정 인덱스를 기준으로 정렬 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>특정 인덱스를 기준으로 정렬</h1>\n<deckgo-highlight-code python  theme=\"one-dark\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">nums = [[&#39;jim&#39;, 4],[&#39;kim&#39;, 3],[&#39;tom&#39;, 2],[&#39;bill&#39;, 1],[&#39;lee&#39;, 5]]\nnums.sort(key=lambda x:x[1]) # 숫자를 기준으로 정렬\nnums\n&gt;&gt; [[&#39;bill&#39;, 1], [&#39;tom&#39;, 2], [&#39;kim&#39;, 3], [&#39;jim&#39;, 4], [&#39;lee&#39;, 5]]</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<deckgo-highlight-code python  theme=\"one-dark\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">from operator import itemgetter\n\nnums = [[&#39;jim&#39;, 4],[&#39;kim&#39;, 3],[&#39;tom&#39;, 2],[&#39;bill&#39;, 1],[&#39;lee&#39;, 5]]\nnums.sort(key=itemgetter(2)) # 같은 역할을한다.\nnums\n&gt;&gt; [[&#39;bill&#39;, 1], [&#39;tom&#39;, 2], [&#39;kim&#39;, 3], [&#39;jim&#39;, 4], [&#39;lee&#39;, 5]]</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h1 id=\"특정-키값을-기준으로-정렬\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B9%EC%A0%95-%ED%82%A4%EA%B0%92%EC%9D%84-%EA%B8%B0%EC%A4%80%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EC%A0%95%EB%A0%AC\" aria-label=\"특정 키값을 기준으로 정렬 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>특정 키값을 기준으로 정렬</h1>\n<deckgo-highlight-code python  theme=\"one-dark\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">nums = [{&#39;name&#39;: &#39;jim&#39;, &#39;index&#39;: 4},{&#39;name&#39;: &#39;kim&#39;, &#39;index&#39;: 3},{&#39;name&#39;: &#39;tom&#39;, &#39;index&#39;: 2},{&#39;name&#39;: &#39;bill&#39;,&#39;index&#39;:  1},{&#39;name&#39;: &#39;lee&#39;, &#39;index&#39;: 5}]\nnums.sort(key=lambda x: x[&#39;name&#39;])# 기준으로 삼고 싶은 어트리뷰트의 이름을 넣는다.\nnums\n&gt;&gt; [{&#39;name&#39;: &#39;bill&#39;,&#39;index&#39;:  1}, {&#39;name&#39;: &#39;tom&#39;, &#39;index&#39;: 2}, {&#39;name&#39;: &#39;kim&#39;, &#39;index&#39;: 3}, {&#39;name&#39;: &#39;jim&#39;, &#39;index&#39;: 4}, {&#39;name&#39;: &#39;lee&#39;, &#39;index&#39;: 5}]</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<deckgo-highlight-code python  theme=\"one-dark\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">from operator import attrgetter\n\nnums = [{&#39;name&#39;: &#39;jim&#39;, &#39;index&#39;: 4},{&#39;name&#39;: &#39;kim&#39;, &#39;index&#39;: 3},{&#39;name&#39;: &#39;tom&#39;, &#39;index&#39;: 2},{&#39;name&#39;: &#39;bill&#39;,&#39;index&#39;:  1},{&#39;name&#39;: &#39;lee&#39;, &#39;index&#39;: 5}]\n\nnums.sort(key=attrgetter(&#39;name&#39;)) # 기준으로 삼고 싶은 어트리뷰트의 이름을 넣는다.\nnums\n&gt;&gt; [{&#39;name&#39;: &#39;bill&#39;,&#39;index&#39;:  1}, {&#39;name&#39;: &#39;tom&#39;, &#39;index&#39;: 2}, {&#39;name&#39;: &#39;kim&#39;, &#39;index&#39;: 3}, {&#39;name&#39;: &#39;jim&#39;, &#39;index&#39;: 4}, {&#39;name&#39;: &#39;lee&#39;, &#39;index&#39;: 5}]</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h1 id=\"오름차순과-내림차순\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%98%A4%EB%A6%84%EC%B0%A8%EC%88%9C%EA%B3%BC-%EB%82%B4%EB%A6%BC%EC%B0%A8%EC%88%9C\" aria-label=\"오름차순과 내림차순 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>오름차순과 내림차순</h1>\n<deckgo-highlight-code python  theme=\"one-dark\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">nums = [4,3,2,1,5]\nnums.sort(reverse=True) # reverse 옵션이 True 인 경우, 내림차순으로 정렬된다.\nnums\n&gt;&gt; [5,4,3,2,1]</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h1 id=\"정렬을-2가지-이상의-기준으로-하고싶을-때\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%95%EB%A0%AC%EC%9D%84-2%EA%B0%80%EC%A7%80-%EC%9D%B4%EC%83%81%EC%9D%98-%EA%B8%B0%EC%A4%80%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%ED%95%98%EA%B3%A0%EC%8B%B6%EC%9D%84-%EB%95%8C\" aria-label=\"정렬을 2가지 이상의 기준으로 하고싶을 때 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>정렬을 2가지 이상의 기준으로 하고싶을 때</h1>\n<deckgo-highlight-code python  theme=\"one-dark\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">l = [(2, 3), (3, 4), (2, 4)]\nl.sort(key = lambda x: (-x[0], -x[1]) )\nprint(l)\nl.sort(key = lambda x: (x[0], -x[1]) )\nprint(l)\n\n&gt;&gt; [(3, 4), (2, 4), (2, 3)] # 각 원소의 0번째 인덱스를 기준으로 내림차순으로 정렬한 후 1번째 인덱스를 기준으로 내림차순하여 2차정렬\n&gt;&gt; [(2, 4), (2, 3), (3, 4)] # 각 원소의 0번째 인덱스를 기준으로 오름차순으로 정렬한 후, 1번째 인덱스를 기준으로 내림차순하여 2차정렬</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<deckgo-highlight-code python  theme=\"one-dark\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">class Student:\n    def __init__(self, name, grade, age):\n        self.name = name\n        self.grade = grade\n        self.age = age\n    def __repr__(self):\n        return repr((self.name, self.grade, self.age))\n&gt;&gt;&gt;\nstudent_objects = [\n    Student(&#39;john&#39;, &#39;A&#39;, 15),\n    Student(&#39;jane&#39;, &#39;B&#39;, 12),\n    Student(&#39;dave&#39;, &#39;B&#39;, 10),\n]\n\ns = sorted(student_objects, key=attrgetter(&#39;age&#39;))     # age 어트리뷰트롤 오름차순으로 정렬한 후\nsorted(s, key=attrgetter(&#39;grade&#39;), reverse=True)       # grade 어트리뷰트를 기준으로 내림차순 2차 정렬\n[(&#39;dave&#39;, &#39;B&#39;, 10), (&#39;jane&#39;, &#39;B&#39;, 12), (&#39;john&#39;, &#39;A&#39;, 15)]</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h3 id=\"참조\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EC%A1%B0\" aria-label=\"참조 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참조</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.python.org/ko/3/howto/sorting.html\">https://docs.python.org/ko/3/howto/sorting.html</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/11850425/custom-python-list-sorting/64329277\">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/11850425/custom-python-list-sorting/64329277</a></li>\n</ul>","htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"프로그래머스에서 "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/42579"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"베스트앨범"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 문제를 풀다가 찾아보게 되었다."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"